  "detailed_description": "The Realistic Ragdoll Sandbox game immerses players in a world of realistic physics and unpredictable interactions. In this virtual universe, ragdoll characters have a unique balance system that allows them to rebalance themselves after receiving impacts or pushes, resulting in extremely realistic animations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/a04129712908bf832f8b9c0a7357ecf9.poster.avif?t=1751128325\" width=684 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/a04129712908bf832f8b9c0a7357ecf9.webm?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/a04129712908bf832f8b9c0a7357ecf9.mp4?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The main feature of this game is the freedom given to players to interact with characters in creative and dynamic ways. They can throw knives, shoot different firearms, and even cause spectacular explosions. Additionally, players can incite fights between characters, allowing punches, kicks, dodges and shots during intense confrontations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/24896bee367d7c577b87a123c33e9e77.poster.avif?t=1751128325\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/24896bee367d7c577b87a123c33e9e77.webm?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/24896bee367d7c577b87a123c33e9e77.mp4?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>One of the most interesting features of the game is the player's ability to take control of any character present, enabling a unique and varied gaming experience in each session. Additionally, players have the freedom to create their own levels, adding an element of customization and creativity to the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/e44542151d6962c61b228e6e9645659c.poster.avif?t=1751128325\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/e44542151d6962c61b228e6e9645659c.webm?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/e44542151d6962c61b228e6e9645659c.mp4?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The Realistic Ragdoll Sandbox game immerses players in a world of realistic physics and unpredictable interactions. In this virtual universe, ragdoll characters have a unique balance system that allows them to rebalance themselves after receiving impacts or pushes, resulting in extremely realistic animations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/a04129712908bf832f8b9c0a7357ecf9.poster.avif?t=1751128325\" width=684 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/a04129712908bf832f8b9c0a7357ecf9.webm?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/a04129712908bf832f8b9c0a7357ecf9.mp4?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The main feature of this game is the freedom given to players to interact with characters in creative and dynamic ways. They can throw knives, shoot different firearms, and even cause spectacular explosions. Additionally, players can incite fights between characters, allowing punches, kicks, dodges and shots during intense confrontations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/24896bee367d7c577b87a123c33e9e77.poster.avif?t=1751128325\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/24896bee367d7c577b87a123c33e9e77.webm?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/24896bee367d7c577b87a123c33e9e77.mp4?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>One of the most interesting features of the game is the player's ability to take control of any character present, enabling a unique and varied gaming experience in each session. Additionally, players have the freedom to create their own levels, adding an element of customization and creativity to the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/e44542151d6962c61b228e6e9645659c.poster.avif?t=1751128325\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/e44542151d6962c61b228e6e9645659c.webm?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048280/extras/e44542151d6962c61b228e6e9645659c.mp4?t=1751128325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
